-- TLT Lottotainment Will Buy 51% of TV Producer in Macau for HK$34.5 Million
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-10-07T14:26:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/tlt-lottotainment-will-buy-51-of-tv-producer-in-macau-for-hk-34-5-million.html
TLT Lottotainment Group Ltd. will pay
HK$34.5 million, in cash and 54.2 million new shares, for a 51
percent stake in a company that produces television programs and
live events in Macau and southeast Asia, the company said in a
Hong Kong stock exchange filing today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  